<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Telegram Bot Jalan.Ai Documentation</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
</head>

<body class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 min-h-screen">

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-10">

        <!-- HEADER -->
        <header class="mb-10">
            <div
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-blue-300 bg-blue-100 px-4 py-1 text-sm text-blue-600 mb-4">
                Documentation
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">
                Telegram Bot Jalan.Ai
            </h1>

            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                Bot ini menyediakan fitur klasifikasi kerusakan jalan.
                Menggunakan model dari website
                <a href="https://jalanai.vercel.app/" class="text-blue-600 font-medium hover:underline">
                    Jalan.Ai
                </a>
                (Tugas Akhir Riyan Fazri Rahman), bot ini memberikan hasil secara real-time melalui unggahan gambar di
                Telegram.
            </p>
        </header>

        <!-- SECTION: BOT COMMAND -->
        <section class="mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 shadow-sm">

                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Perintah Bot Telegram</h2>

                <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                    <li>📌 <code>/start</code> → Informasi dasar bot</li>
                    <li>📊 <code>/status</code> → Status server model</li>
                    <li>📜 <code>/history</code> → 10 hasil klasifikasi terakhir</li>
                    <li>📷 Upload gambar → klasifikasi otomatis</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
                    Bot aktif di:
                    <a href="https://t.me/tesryn_bot" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">
                        @tesryn_bot
                    </a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- SECTION: API -->
        <section class="mb-10">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-6 shadow-sm">

                <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Penggunaan API</h2>

                <p class="text-slate-600 mb-3">
                    Bot ini menggunakan API dari endpoint berikut:
                </p>

                <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                    <code class="text-blue-600 break-all">
                        <a href="https://jalanai-api.vercel.app/api/classification" target="_blank" class="hover:underline">
                            https://jalanai-api.vercel.app/api/classification
                        </a>
                    </code>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <footer class="text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
            © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Jalan.Ai ChatBot | Riyan Fazri Rahman
        </footer>

    </div>

</body>

</html>